<div class="list-pages-item">


<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00059/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>项目描述：</strong><span style="text-decoration: line-through;">一支法制MAS36步枪，质感异常柔软且具有麦香味</span>一条法式长棍面包，具有认知危害，可使任何观察到该项目的人类认为该项目是一支法制MAS36步枪。<br />
<strong>回收日期：</strong>20██/██/██<br />
<strong>回收地点：</strong>Site-CN-21员工食堂<br />
<strong>当前状态：</strong>已被食用<br />
<strong>笔记：</strong><em>今日乳法</em>——Dr.Jackson</p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span id="u-credit-00059" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00059" target="_blank">编辑</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00059-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/miku1314" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4546338); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4546338&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610226421" alt="miku1314" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4546338)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/miku1314" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4546338); return false;">miku1314</a></span></p>
<p><strong>发布日期：</strong><span class="odate time_1586756541 format_%25Y-%25m-%25d">13 Apr 2020 05:42</span></p>
